{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":817,"text":"I have been a police officer\nfor a very, very long time."},{"time":3492,"text":"And you see these notes in my hand\nbecause I'm also a black preacher."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9305,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":11012,"text":"And if you know anything\nabout black preachers,"},{"time":13251,"text":"we'll close, and then we'll keep\ngoing for another 20 minutes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16487,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17548,"text":"So I need this to keep\npushing this thing forward."},{"time":19965,"text":"I've been a police officer\nfor a very long time,"},{"time":22238,"text":"and I mean I predated technology."},{"time":23842,"text":"I'm talking about before pagers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25462,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26719,"text":"Laugh if you want to,\nbut I'm telling the truth."},{"time":29004,"text":"I predate War on Our Fellow Man --\nI mean, War on Drugs."},{"time":33730,"text":"I predate all of that."},{"time":35855,"text":"I predate so much"},{"time":37033,"text":"and I've been through ebbs and flows"},{"time":38840,"text":"and I've been through good and bad times,"},{"time":41231,"text":"and still I absolutely love\nbeing a police officer."},{"time":46207,"text":"I love being a police officer\nbecause it's always been a calling for me"},{"time":49982,"text":"and never a job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52219,"text":"And even with that,"},{"time":54538,"text":"my personal truth is that\nlaw enforcement is in a crisis."},{"time":59616,"text":"It's an invisible crisis,"},{"time":61154,"text":"and it has been for many, many years."},{"time":64787,"text":"Even though we in law enforcement say,"},{"time":66680,"text":"\"You know what?\nWe can't arrest our way out of this.\""},{"time":71258,"text":"We say in law enforcement things like,"},{"time":73093,"text":"\"Yeah, it's illegal to profile.\""},{"time":76008,"text":"You know what?"},{"time":77190,"text":"In law enforcement, we even agree\nthat we have to adopt this thinking"},{"time":80572,"text":"and become more oriented\nto community policing."},{"time":82801,"text":"And yet all the while, still,"},{"time":85735,"text":"we continue in the same vein,"},{"time":87956,"text":"the same vein that contradicts\neverything that we just admitted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93131,"text":"And so that's the reason for me,\nseveral years ago."},{"time":96313,"text":"Because I was tired of the racism,\nI was tired of discrimination,"},{"time":99432,"text":"I was tired of the \"-isms\"\nand the schisms."},{"time":102049,"text":"I was just so tired."},{"time":103904,"text":"I was tired of the vicious cycle,"},{"time":106081,"text":"and I was tired of it even\nin the beloved agency"},{"time":109334,"text":"in the department that I still love today."},{"time":112771,"text":"And so my wife and I, we sat down"},{"time":114924,"text":"and we decided and we targeted\na date that we would retire."},{"time":118130,"text":"We would retire and I would\ngo off into the sunset,"},{"time":120758,"text":"maybe do ministry full time,\nlove my wife a long time."},{"time":123615,"text":"Y'all know what I'm talking about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126709,"text":"But we decided that I would retire."},{"time":128456,"text":"But then there was a higher power than I."},{"time":132492,"text":"There was a love for the city"},{"time":135384,"text":"that I loved, that I grew up in,\nthat I was educated in --"},{"time":138609,"text":"a city that pulled my heart\nback into the system."},{"time":142959,"text":"So we didn't retire."},{"time":144916,"text":"We didn't retire"},{"time":146334,"text":"and so what happened was,"},{"time":148822,"text":"over the next -- I would say,\n18 months, 19 months,"},{"time":153050,"text":"I had this passion to implement\nsome radical policing."},{"time":157393,"text":"And so now, over the next 19 months,"},{"time":159148,"text":"I shifted, and I transcended\nfrom being a drug sergeant --"},{"time":164277,"text":"ready to retire as a drug sergeant --"},{"time":166865,"text":"and went from level to level to level,"},{"time":168723,"text":"until I find myself\nas a district commander,"},{"time":171176,"text":"commander of the worst district\nin Baltimore city."},{"time":174453,"text":"We call it the Eastern District,"},{"time":176178,"text":"the most violent district,"},{"time":177812,"text":"the most impoverished district --"},{"time":179543,"text":"46 percent unemployment in that district."},{"time":184018,"text":"National rating at that time,"},{"time":186262,"text":"national rating, the AIDS\nand the tuberculosis [rating],"},{"time":189258,"text":"was always on the top 10 list"},{"time":191683,"text":"for zip codes for cities\nacross the nation,"},{"time":194730,"text":"or just zip codes across the nation."},{"time":196493,"text":"The top 10 -- I didn't say state,\nI didn't say city --"},{"time":199135,"text":"that little neighborhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201911,"text":"And I said, you know what?\nWe gotta do something different."},{"time":204738,"text":"We gotta do something different.\nWe gotta think radical."},{"time":207422,"text":"We gotta think outside the box."},{"time":209730,"text":"And so in order to bring change\nthat I desperately wanted"},{"time":212436,"text":"and I desperately felt in my heart,"},{"time":214167,"text":"I had to start listening\nto that inner spirit."},{"time":216480,"text":"I had to start listening\nto that man on the inside"},{"time":218937,"text":"that went against everything\nthat I had been trained to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222772,"text":"But we still did it."},{"time":224190,"text":"We still did it because we listened\nto that inner spirit,"},{"time":226911,"text":"because I realized this:"},{"time":228196,"text":"if I was to see real police reform"},{"time":232269,"text":"in the communities that I had\nauthority over for public safety,"},{"time":236690,"text":"we had to change our stinkin' thinkin'."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240728,"text":"We had to change it."},{"time":241905,"text":"And so what we did\nis we started to think holistically"},{"time":244652,"text":"and not paramilitarily."},{"time":246538,"text":"So we thought differently."},{"time":248819,"text":"And we started to realize"},{"time":250042,"text":"that it could never be\nand never should have been"},{"time":252376,"text":"us versus them."},{"time":254910,"text":"And so I decided to come\nto that intersection"},{"time":257142,"text":"where I could meet all classes,\nall races, all creeds, all colors;"},{"time":260387,"text":"where I would meet the businesses\nand the faith-based,"},{"time":262952,"text":"and the eds, the meds,"},{"time":264262,"text":"and I would meet all the people"},{"time":265794,"text":"that made up the communities\nthat I had authority over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269205,"text":"So I met them and I began to listen."},{"time":271189,"text":"See, police have a problem."},{"time":272665,"text":"Off the top, we want to bring\nthings into the community"},{"time":275284,"text":"and come up with these extravagant\nstrategies and deployments,"},{"time":278276,"text":"but we never talk\nto the community about them."},{"time":280475,"text":"And we shove them into the community\nand say, \"Take that.\""},{"time":283806,"text":"But we said we'd get rid\nof that stinkin' thinkin',"},{"time":286227,"text":"so we talked to our communities."},{"time":287799,"text":"We said, \"This is your community table."},{"time":289691,"text":"We'll pull up a chair.\nWe want to hear from you."},{"time":291978,"text":"What's going to work in your community?\""},{"time":293942,"text":"And then some great things\nstarted to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296095,"text":"See, here's the thing:"},{"time":297270,"text":"I had to figure out a way to shift\n130 cops that were under my tutelage"},{"time":303014,"text":"from being occupiers of communities"},{"time":305150,"text":"to being partners."},{"time":307355,"text":"I had to figure out how to do that."},{"time":309071,"text":"Because here's the crazy thing:"},{"time":311074,"text":"in law enforcement, we have evolved\ninto something incredible."},{"time":314743,"text":"Listen, we have become great protectors."},{"time":316704,"text":"We know how to protect you."},{"time":318909,"text":"But we have exercised that arm\nso much, so very much."},{"time":322972,"text":"If I was a natural police department"},{"time":326162,"text":"and I represented a police department,"},{"time":328067,"text":"you would see this incredible,\nbeautiful, 23-inch arm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330980,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333607,"text":"It's pretty, ain't it? It's cut up."},{"time":336641,"text":"No fat on it. Mmm it look good.\nIt just look good!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339592,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341750,"text":"That's a great arm -- protection!"},{"time":343675,"text":"That's who we are, but we've exercised\nit so much sometimes"},{"time":347255,"text":"that it has led to abuse."},{"time":350008,"text":"It's led to coldness and callousness\nand dehumanized us."},{"time":354941,"text":"And we've forgotten"},{"time":356117,"text":"the mantra across this nation"},{"time":357554,"text":"is to protect and serve."},{"time":360068,"text":"Y'all don't know that? Protect and serve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362068,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363093,"text":"So you look at the other arm,"},{"time":364522,"text":"and then you look at it\nand ... there it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366681,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":368267,"text":"You know, it's kinda weak."},{"time":370926,"text":"It looks sickly."},{"time":372972,"text":"It's withering and it's dying"},{"time":375861,"text":"because we've invested so much\nin our protective arm."},{"time":379302,"text":"But we forgot to treat our communities"},{"time":382183,"text":"like they're our customers;"},{"time":384026,"text":"like they're our sons and daughters,\nour brothers and sisters,"},{"time":387015,"text":"our mothers and fathers."},{"time":388600,"text":"And so somehow, along the way,"},{"time":390873,"text":"we've gotten out of balance."},{"time":392958,"text":"And because we are a proud profession,"},{"time":395952,"text":"it is very hard for us to look\nin the mirror and see our mistakes."},{"time":399117,"text":"It's even harder to make a change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401775,"text":"And so, as I try to hurry\nand get through this,"},{"time":405204,"text":"I need to say this:"},{"time":406389,"text":"it's not just law enforcement, though."},{"time":408818,"text":"Because every one of us\nmakes up a community."},{"time":411674,"text":"Everybody makes up a community."},{"time":413678,"text":"And as communities -- can I say this? --"},{"time":415630,"text":"we have put too much responsibility\non law enforcement."},{"time":420261,"text":"Too much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421443,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":426706,"text":"And then we have the audacity\nand the nerve to get upset"},{"time":429377,"text":"with law enforcement\nwhen we take action."},{"time":432265,"text":"There is no way in the world"},{"time":434615,"text":"that we, as a community,\nshould be calling the police"},{"time":438182,"text":"for kids playing ball in the street."},{"time":442071,"text":"No way in the world that we\nshould be calling the police"},{"time":444831,"text":"because my neighbor's\nmusic is up too loud,"},{"time":446941,"text":"because his dog came over\nto my yard and did a number two;"},{"time":449719,"text":"there's no way we should\nbe calling the police."},{"time":452264,"text":"But we have surrendered\nso much of our responsibility."},{"time":454930,"text":"Listen, when I was a little boy\ncoming up in Baltimore --"},{"time":458088,"text":"and listen, we played\nrough in the street --"},{"time":460249,"text":"I ain't never see the police\ncome and break us up."},{"time":463026,"text":"You know who came? It was the elders."},{"time":464975,"text":"It was the parental figures\nin the community."},{"time":467440,"text":"It was those guardians,\nit was that village mentality."},{"time":470051,"text":"They came and said, \"Stop that!\"\nand \"Do this.\" and \"Stop that.\""},{"time":473689,"text":"We had mentors throughout\nall of the community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477769,"text":"So it takes all of us, all of us."},{"time":480620,"text":"And when I say community,"},{"time":481844,"text":"I'm talking about everything\nthat makes up a community, even --"},{"time":484895,"text":"listen, because I'm a preacher,\nI'm very hard on the churches,"},{"time":487850,"text":"because I believe the churches\ntoo often have become MIA,"},{"time":490621,"text":"missing in action."},{"time":491802,"text":"I believe they have shifted\nover the last 10, 20 years"},{"time":494394,"text":"from being community churches,"},{"time":495894,"text":"where you walk outside your door,\nround the corner and you're in church."},{"time":499386,"text":"They shifted from that and became\ncommuter churches."},{"time":502270,"text":"So you now have churches who have\nbecome disconnected by default"},{"time":506754,"text":"from the very community\nwhere they're planted."},{"time":510060,"text":"And they don't take care\nof that community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513153,"text":"I could go on and on,\nbut I really need to wrap this up."},{"time":515845,"text":"Community and policing:"},{"time":518520,"text":"we've all lost that precious gift,\nand I call it relational equity."},{"time":523498,"text":"We've lost it with one another."},{"time":525445,"text":"It's not somebody else's fault --"},{"time":527484,"text":"it's all of our fault."},{"time":529371,"text":"We all take responsibility in this."},{"time":531361,"text":"But I say this: it's not too late\nfor all of us to build our cities"},{"time":534586,"text":"and nation to make it great again."},{"time":536248,"text":"It is never too late."},{"time":537431,"text":"It is never too late."},{"time":539428,"text":"You see, after three years"},{"time":540853,"text":"of my four-and-a-half-year\ncommandship in that district,"},{"time":544115,"text":"three years in,"},{"time":545293,"text":"after putting pastors\nin the car with my police"},{"time":547996,"text":"because I knew this --\nit's a little secret --"},{"time":550195,"text":"I knew this:"},{"time":551378,"text":"it was hard to stay a nasty police officer"},{"time":554067,"text":"while you're riding around\nwith a clergy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556192,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":558398,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566476,"text":"You'd be getting in and out of the car,\nlooking to your right, talking about:"},{"time":570029,"text":"\"Father, forgive me, for I have sinned,\"\nall day long -- you can't do it!"},{"time":573589,"text":"So we came up with some\nincredible initiatives,"},{"time":575866,"text":"engagements for our community\nand police to build that trust back."},{"time":579385,"text":"We began to deal with our youth"},{"time":580968,"text":"and with those who we consider\nare on the wrong side of the fence."},{"time":584170,"text":"We knew we had an economic problem,"},{"time":585927,"text":"so we began to create jobs."},{"time":587443,"text":"We knew there was sickness\nin our community"},{"time":589515,"text":"and they didn't have access\nto proper medical care,"},{"time":592033,"text":"so we'd partner up."},{"time":593216,"text":"We got to that intersection\nand partnered up"},{"time":595313,"text":"with anybody that wanted\nto partner with us"},{"time":597424,"text":"and talked about\nwhat we needed holistically,"},{"time":599615,"text":"never thinking about the crime."},{"time":601152,"text":"Because at the end of the day,"},{"time":602871,"text":"if we took care\nof the needs of the people,"},{"time":604958,"text":"if we got to the root cause,"},{"time":607251,"text":"the crime would take care of itself."},{"time":610599,"text":"It would take care of itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612089,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617897,"text":"And so, after three years\nof a four-and-a-half-year stint,"},{"time":622665,"text":"we looked back and we looked over"},{"time":624365,"text":"and found out that we were\nat a 40-year historical low:"},{"time":627754,"text":"our crime numbers, our homicides --"},{"time":630659,"text":"everything had dropped\ndown, back to the 1970s."},{"time":633140,"text":"And it might go back further,"},{"time":634580,"text":"but the problem is, we only\nstarted keeping data since 1970."},{"time":637521,"text":"Forty-year crime low, so much so,\nI had other commanders call me,"},{"time":640641,"text":"\"Hey Mel, whatcha doin', man?"},{"time":642082,"text":"Whatcha doin'? We gotta get some of that!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":644210,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645649,"text":"And so we gave them some of that."},{"time":648968,"text":"And in a short period of time,"},{"time":650444,"text":"the city went to a 30-year crime low."},{"time":653181,"text":"For the first time in 30 years,\nwe fell, Baltimore city,"},{"time":655854,"text":"to under 200 homicides -- 197 to be exact."},{"time":658242,"text":"And we celebrated,"},{"time":659425,"text":"because we had learned\nto become great servers,"},{"time":663132,"text":"become great servers first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664893,"text":"But I gotta tell you this:\nthese last few years,"},{"time":668607,"text":"as much as we had learned"},{"time":670856,"text":"to become great proactive police officers"},{"time":673827,"text":"and great relational police officers\nrather than reactive,"},{"time":677612,"text":"these last years have disappointed me."},{"time":680710,"text":"They have broken my heart."},{"time":682644,"text":"The uprising still hurts."},{"time":685584,"text":"It still hurts my heart,"},{"time":687294,"text":"because truly I believe\nthat it should've never happened."},{"time":691014,"text":"I believe it should've never happened"},{"time":692831,"text":"if we were allowed to continue\nalong the vein that we were in,"},{"time":695799,"text":"servicing our community,"},{"time":697503,"text":"treating them like human beings,\ntreating them with respect,"},{"time":700463,"text":"loving on them first."},{"time":702670,"text":"If we continued in that vein,"},{"time":704854,"text":"it would've never happened."},{"time":706727,"text":"But somehow, we went back\nto business as usual."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709956,"text":"But I'm excited again!"},{"time":712164,"text":"I'm excited again, because now\nwe have a police commissioner"},{"time":715533,"text":"who not only talks\nabout community policing,"},{"time":719800,"text":"but he absolutely understands it,"},{"time":722142,"text":"and more importantly, he embraces it."},{"time":724238,"text":"So I'm very excited now."},{"time":725981,"text":"Listen, I'm excited about Baltimore today,"},{"time":728954,"text":"because we, as many cities,\nI believe shall rise from the ashes."},{"time":733973,"text":"I believe -- I truly believe --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":736886,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":737932,"text":"that we will be great again."},{"time":740639,"text":"I believe,"},{"time":742470,"text":"as we continue to wrap arms\nand continue to say,"},{"time":745565,"text":"\"We're in this together,\""},{"time":746787,"text":"because it's not just an intersection:"},{"time":748654,"text":"once we meet, we now gotta get\non the same path for the same goals,"},{"time":752312,"text":"and this city will become great again."},{"time":754384,"text":"This nation will become great again."},{"time":756369,"text":"Because we have the same goal:\nwe all want peace."},{"time":758812,"text":"We all want respect for one another."},{"time":760570,"text":"We all want love."},{"time":761744,"text":"And I believe we are back on that road,"},{"time":763660,"text":"and I'm so excited about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765054,"text":"So listen, I thank you for giving me\na few minutes of your time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768426,"text":"God bless you all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":769680,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":770705,"text":"God bless you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771880,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}